text: Cisita Joity Jansen (born 31 October 1990) is a German female badminton player and of Indonesian origin. In 2005, she placed third at the Singapore Cheers tournament, and recruited by PB Djarum badminton club in 2007. In 2013, she became the runner-up of Slovenia International tournament in mixed doubles event with her brother Jones Rafli Jansen.
